data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  This Condo would be the perfect INVESTMENT property.  A must see three bedroom, two and a half bathroom condo.  It is set right above the auto mall with access to shopping and multiple recreational activities nearby.  This condo has such charm and feel of home inside.  The back yard has is it's own little oasis to relax and enjoy the evening.  There is a one car garage with additional parking in front.  In the process of verifying the HOA condo fees.  The condo is vacant so it is easy to show.  Additional pictures in the next couple of days.  Please call or text Lynnette Avery at 406-439-7215 or your real estate professional for a showing.
